            . The pin was in a bureau in the cook's room, among some papers of no value; I intended to make a present of it; I went to look for it and found the lock of my bureau broke, and the pin taken away; the prisoner was my servant; he was gone away; I got him taken up; he confessed that he broke open the lock, took the pin, and gave it to his mother.</p>



